Test Case ID: 19
Run Result ID: 1
Horizontal Slider

----------------
Summary:
Test and observe the horizontal slider, check the value or number located to the right of the slider if how specific it is.

Setup:
https://the-internet.herokuapp.com/horizontal_slider 

Steps:
1. Click the blue small circle within the slider.
2. Click and drag it to the right.

Result:
As the user clicks and drags the point to his desired spot the value or the number changes depending on how far from the initial point it was placed. If placed at the corner right of the slider it will display the maximum number of the sliders value, the very left corner on the other hand is a zero value.